column5: PLEASE HELP! Lost Pelican 60 sled cover about an hour ago on north shore Kemp Bay Lake Simcoe.  Wind direction was straight towards Bear Point on the South shore. If found please text or call 705-795-8121. Thank you to anyone who can help
Well it will probably be in beaverton in 10 minutes.
lol I was thinking of driving around and maybe meeting it there. Punch a few holes for perch while I'm at it lol. But the gas money will be the same as a new cover
That sucks. I have the same one, always have 2 bungees securing it down to the sled... Or did it blow away while off the sled lol?

It was laying inside the sled while we were in the hut, hiding from the wind lol. It has been "re-covered!" Thanks to the guys fishing in the open in front of me for snagging it and getting it to Todd  for me! Thanks guys, fisher-people kick ass!
How was the fishing? I know where you were, satilite image I have.LOL  Glad you got it back dude.
Awesome ending.  X2  And yes how was the fishing???  Dan.

Ya fish?  Let's see them.  You want your cover back and I'm good enough for you to ask that but you ain't gunna show me the fish.  Come on man on this screen is the only fish I get to see.   Hurry up.
Let's just say I'm glad I have two more days to give em hell! lol I need redemption and a good meal!
